um\"\n|-\n| 2010 || ''[[Hubworld]]'' || Herself || 1 episode<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/followbailee/status/18021973590286336 |title=Twitter / Bailee Madison: Katie and I will be on the |publisher=Twitter.com |date=December 23, 2010 |accessdate=January 28, 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2010-2012 || ''[[R.L. Stine's The Haunting Hour]]'' || Lilly Carbo / Jenny / Becky || 4 episodes; <br> Guest role (Seasons 1-3)\n|-\n|  2011 || ''[[Wizards of Waverly Place]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tvguide.com/News/Exclusive-Disney-Channel-1024328.aspx?rss=breakingnews6|\nauthor=Megan Walsh-Boyle|title=Exclusive: Disney Channel Announces Season 4 of Wizards of Waverly Place|work=tvguide.com|accessdate=April 17, 2011}}</ref> || [[Max Russo|Maxine Russo]] || 6 episodes; <br> Recurring role (Season 4)\n|-\n| 2011 || ''[[Chase (2010 TV series)|Chase]]'' || Zoe || Episode: \"Father Figure\"\n|-\n| 2011 || ''[[Powers (FX TV series)|Powers]]'' || Calista || Pilot<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.deadline.com/2011/06/pilot-castings-usas-overunder-finds-female-lead-young-actress-joins-powers/| author=Nellie Andreeva |title=Pilot Castings: USA's 'Over/Under' Finds Female Lead, Young Actress Joins 'Powers'|work=deadline.com|accessdate=June 16, 2011| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110706145249/http://www.deadline.com/2011/06/pilot-castings-usas-overunder-finds-female-lead-young-actress-joins-powers/| archivedate= July 6, 2011 | url-status= live}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2012\u201313, 2016 || ''[[Once Upon a Time (TV series)|Once Upon a Time]]'' || Young [[Snow White]] || 4 episodes; <br> Guest role (Seasons 1-2 & 5)\n|-\n| 2013 || ''[[Holliston (TV series)|Holliston]]'' || Bailee || Episode \"Rock the Cradle\"\n|-\n| 2013\u20132014 || ''[[Trophy Wife (TV series)|Trophy Wife]]'' || Hillary Harrison || 21 episodes; <br> Main role (Season 1)\n|-\n| 2014\u20132016 || | ''[[The Fosters (2013 TV series)|The Fosters]]'' || Sophia Quinn || 11 episodes; <br> Recurring role (Seasons 2-4)\n|-\n|2014 || ''[[American Dad!]]'' || Unknown || Episode: \"Roger Passes the Bar\"\n|-\n| 2015\u20132019 || ''[[Good Witch (TV series)|Good Witch]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hallmarkchannel.com/good-witch/cast|title=Cast of Good Witch|website=Hallmark Channel}}</ref> || Grace Russell || 55 episodes; <br> Main role (Seasons 1-5)\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Mulaney]]'' || Ruby || Episode: \"Ruby\"\n|}\n\n===Music videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Artist\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n| 2017\n| \"Love You So\"\n| Alex Lange\n| Alex's Girlfriend\n| Lead role\n|-\n| 2019\n| \"Foolish\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Meghan Trainor]]\n| Meghan's Party Guest\n| Cameo\n|-\n| 2019\n| \"All the Ways\"\n| The Bear's Love Interest\n| Lead role\n|-\n| 2019\n| \"Love Again\"\n| [[New Hope Club]]\n| Blake's Girlfriend\n| Lead role\n|-\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-  style=\"background:#b0c4de; text-align:center;\"\n! Year !! Association !! Category !! Nominated work !! Result !! {{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n| rowspan=5 | 2008 || rowspan=4 | [[Young Artist Awards]] || [[29th Young Artist Awards#Best Performance in a Feature Film - Young Actress Ten and Under|Best Performance in a Feature Film Young Actress Age Ten or Younger]] || rowspan=2 | ''Bridge to Terabithia'' || {{won}} ||<ref name=\"Young Artist Awards 3\">{{cite web|url=http://www.youngartistawards.org/noms29.html |title=29th Annual Young Artist Awards |accessdate=March 31, 2011 |work=YoungArtistAwards.org |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080706161000/http://www.youngartistawards.org/noms29.html |archivedate=July 6, 2008 }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[29th Young Artist Awards#Best Performance in a Feature Film - Young Ensemble Cast|Best Performance in a Feature Film \u2013 Young Ensemble Cast]] || {{won}} ||<ref name=\"Young Artist Awards 3\"/>\n|-\n| [[29th Young Artist Awards#Best Performance in a TV series - Guest Starring Young Actress|Best Performance in a TV Series Guest