 appearance in [[FA Community Shield]], one appearance in [[UEFA Super Cup]], two appearances in [[FIFA Club World Cup]]|name=|group=}}||0||35||3\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total\n!264||25||18||0||22||1||51||2||4||0||359||28\n|-\n!colspan=3|Career total\n!345||30||24||0||27||2||51||2||4||0||451||34\n|}\n\n{{notelist}}\n\n===International===\n{{updated|match played 14 October 2019}}<ref>{{NFT player |id=40555 |name=Henderson, Jordan |accessdate=14 October 2019}}<br />{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49929616 |title=Czech Republic 2\u20131 England |first=Phil |last=McNulty |website=BBC Sport |date=11 October 2019 |accessdate=11 October 2019}}<br />{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49955900 |title=Bulgaria 0\u20136 England |first=Phil |last=McNulty |website=BBC Sport |date=14 October 2019 |accessdate=14 October 2019}}</ref>\n\n{| class=wikitable style=text-align:center\n|+ Appearances and goals by national team and year\n|-\n!National team!!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=9|[[England national football team|England]]\n|2010||1||0\n|-\n|2012||4||0\n|-\n|2013||2||0\n|-\n|2014||11||0\n|-\n|2015||4||0\n|-\n|2016||10||0\n|-\n|2017||4||0\n|-\n|2018||12||0\n|-\n|2019||7||0\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total||55||0\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n'''Liverpool'''\n*[[Football League Cup]]: [[2011\u201312 Football League Cup|2011\u201312]];<ref name=2012LC/> runner-up: [[2015\u201316 Football League Cup|2015\u201316]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35624164 |title=Liverpool 1\u20131 Manchester City |first=Phil |last=McNulty |website=BBC Sport |date=28 February 2016 |accessdate=20 December 2017}}</ref>\n*[[UEFA Champions League]]: [[2018\u201319 UEFA Champions League|2018\u201319]];<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/48368443 |title=Tottenham Hotspur 0\u20132 Liverpool |first=Phil |last=McNulty |website=BBC Sport |date=1 June 2019 |accessdate=1 June 2019}}</ref> runner-up: [[2017\u201318 UEFA Champions League|2017\u201318]]<re