ers (darts)|5R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2013 World Masters (darts)|6R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:yellow;\"|[[2014 World Masters (darts)|SF]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:lime;\"|'''[[2015 World Masters (darts)|W]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:lime;\"|'''[[2016 World Masters (darts)|W]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffebcd;\"|[[2017 World Masters (darts)|QF]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:thistle;\"|[[2018 World Masters (darts)|F]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|PDC\n|-\n| style=\"background:#efefef;\"| {{Nowrap|[[Finder Darts Masters]]}}\n| colspan=\"11\" style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|DNQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:lime;\"|'''[[2015 Zuiderduin Masters|W]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:lime;\"|'''[[Zuiderduin Masters|W]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[Zuiderduin Masters|RR]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:lime;\"|'''[[Zuiderduin Masters|W]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|PDC\n|}\n\n'''PDC'''\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:50%; margin:0\"\n|-\n! Tournament !! 2005 !! 2006 !! 2007 !! 2008 !! 2009 !! 2010 !! 2011 !! 2012 !! 2013 !! 2014 !! 2015 !! 2016 !! 2017 !! 2018 !! 2019 !! 2020\n|-\n| style=\"background:#efefef;\"| [[PDC World Darts Championship|PDC World Championship]]\n| colspan=\"15\" style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|Non-PDC\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffebcd;\"|[[2020 PDC World Darts Championship|QF]]\n|-\n| style=\"background:#efefef;\"| [[UK Open]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2005 UK Open|2R]]\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|DNQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2009 UK Open|3R]]\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|DNQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2012 UK Open|Prel.]]\n| colspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;